works.description: Designed by artist Masataka Kurashina, in collaboration with local design store TOKYO CULTUARTS by BEAMS, the Flame Frame is something we won’t recommend to any biker out there. The Flame Frame is a stylish fire flame-style retro helmet sculpture, which is being marketed as a collectible item for design lovers. Available in two colors from JapanTrendShop for a cool $890, the limited edition Flame Frame comes signed by the designer in a special box.
